---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const base = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---

<BaseLayout title="AI" description="Claude Code Skill 工具箱、AI 工作流搭建、Obsidian 知识管理实践。6 个自创 Skill，从实际项目中长出来。">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1>🤖 AI 摸鱼</h1>
    <p>Claude Code · Skill 工具箱 · 工作流自动化</p>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <section class="section-block intro">
      <p>我把 AI 当作生产力工具来用——不只是聊天，而是搭建工作流、开发 Skill、让 AI 帮我完成完整的工程任务。以下 6 个 Skill 都是从真实项目中长出来的。</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>🏗️ 自创 Skill（6 个）</h2>
      <div class="skill-grid">

        <!-- hongmeng -->
        <a href={`${base}ai/skills/hongmeng/`} class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">📱</span>
            <div>
              <h3>hongmeng</h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">Web App → 鸿蒙原生 ArkTS → AppGallery 上架</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>完整的鸿蒙上架流水线：脚手架 → 构建签名 → AGC 提交。支撑 SOSO App 成功上架华为应用市场。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>ArkTS</span><span>AGC</span><span>DevEco</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- app-builder -->
        <a href={`${base}ai/skills/app-builder/`} class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">📦</span>
            <div>
              <h3>app-builder</h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">HTML/CSS/JS → 签名 Android APK</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Nitron 脚手架 → Gradle 构建 → v1+v2+v3 三重签名。踩坑：APK 内 fetch() 对 file:// 无效、WebView 不支持 IndexedDB。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>Gradle</span><span>Android</span><span>APK</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- green-power-calc -->
        <a href={`${base}ai/skills/green-power-calc/`} class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">⚡</span>
            <div>
              <h3>green-power-calc</h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">1192 号文三模式绿电电费计算器</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>传统两部制 / 绿电两部制 / 绿电容量制一键对比。含授权管理、每日限额、永久白名单。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>政策模型</span><span>GitHub Pages</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- wechat-daily -->
        <a href={`${base}ai/skills/wechat-daily/`} class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">📰</span>
            <div>
              <h3>wechat-daily</h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">公众号「王炸小纸条」每日日报自动生成</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>自动搜索新能源 & AI 动态 → 编译为格式化日报 → 注入公众号草稿。用户只需在手机上点发布。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>自动化</span><span>微信公众号</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- agent-reach -->
        <a href="https://github.com/Panniantong/Agent-Reach" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">🌐</span>
            <div>
              <h3>agent-reach <span class="external-icon">↗</span></h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">14+ 互联网平台统一读/搜接口</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>Python CLI + 库，给 AI Agent 提供 Twitter、Reddit、YouTube 等平台的统一接口。独立开源项目。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>Python</span><span>开源</span><span>API</span>
          </div>
        </a>

        <!-- agently-mail -->
        <a href={`${base}ai/skills/agently-mail/`} class="skill-card card skill-card-link">
          <div class="skill-header">
            <span class="skill-icon">✉️</span>
            <div>
              <h3>agently-mail</h3>
              <span class="skill-desc">自然语言操作 QQ 邮箱</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p>OAuth 授权后，Claude Code 可发送、回复、转发、搜索、读取、下载邮件附件。</p>
          <div class="skill-tags">
            <span>邮件</span><span>CLI</span>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>📖 案例研究</h2>
      <div class="case-card card">
        <h3>SOSO App 鸿蒙上架全流程</h3>
        <p>一个 PWA 原型，经历 ArkTS 工程重构、DevEco 构建、证书签名、AGC 提交、审核驳回修复，最终成功上架华为应用市场。踩过的坑：AGC 只要 .app 不要 .hap、entry 模块需独立资源文件、API level 有上限。</p>
        <div class="case-tags">
          <span>hongmeng</span><span>app-builder</span><span>frontend-design</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section-block">
      <h2>🔗 高频组合套路</h2>
      <div class="combo-grid">
        <div class="combo card">
          <code>frontend-design → hongmeng</code>
          <span>Web 设计 → 鸿蒙上架全流程</span>
        </div>
        <div class="combo card">
          <code>frontend-design → app-builder</code>
          <span>Web 设计 → APK 快捷分发</span>
        </div>
        <div class="combo card">
          <code>wechat-daily + web-access</code>
          <span>日报采集 → 公众号草稿自动化</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-header {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 100px 0 40px;
  }

  .page-header h1 { margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .page-header p { font-size: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary); }

  .content {
    max-width: var(--max-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--content-padding);
  }

  .section-block {
    margin-bottom: 48px;
  }

  .section-block h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .intro p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.9;
  }

  .skill-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(360px, 1fr));
    gap: 14px;
  }

  .skill-card {
    padding: 22px 24px;
    display: block;
    color: inherit;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .skill-card-link:hover {
    opacity: 1;
  }

  .skill-card-link:hover h3 {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .skill-header {
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
    align-items: flex-start;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .skill-icon {
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    line-height: 1.2;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .skill-header h3 {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    color: var(--accent-blue);
    transition: color 0.2s;
  }

  .external-icon {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-placeholder);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .skill-card-link:hover .external-icon {
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .skill-desc {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
  }

  .skill-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .skill-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 6px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .skill-tags span {
    background: #f0f0f0;
    color: var(--text-tertiary);
    font-size: 0.7rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 8px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .case-card {
    padding: 24px;
  }

  .case-card h3 {
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .case-card p {
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .case-tags {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .case-tags span {
    background: var(--accent-blue-bg);
    color: var(--accent-blue-text);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    padding: 2px 10px;
    border-radius: 100px;
  }

  .combo-grid {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 10px;
  }

  .combo {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    padding: 14px 20px;
  }

  .combo code {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
    background: var(--bg-primary);
    padding: 4px 10px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .combo span {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .skill-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
